ted for machine learning\npurposes. Numerical results show the efficacy of the proposed algorithm under\nimperfect CSI and spatially correlated channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 16:27:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-26"}
