rough case studies performed by domain experts\nusing data generated over the five-year deployment of a one-of-a-kind sensor\nnetwork in New York City.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 22:02:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
