 stars, which were formed in the more massive host itself.\nThere are also global differences between the three galaxies studied here, of\nup to $\\sim 0.3\\ \\mathrm{dex}$ in the IMF parameter $\\xi$. We find no local\ndynamical or chemical property which alone can fully account for the IMF\nvariations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 23:16:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-15"}
