ates between the \\emph{area-law} and \\emph{volume-law} for a scalar field\nwith stable modes or zero-modes. We then provide a qualitative discussion of\nthe above effects for scalar fields in cosmological and black-hole space-times.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 May 2022 13:20:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2022 05:19:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-19"}
